elements.name: Verify Category selection is a sub-category

steps.name: user is logged in as admin
user is on the Plants List page
user clicks on "Add a Plant" button
user should be navigated to "Add Plants" page
the category dropdown should contains sub-categories "Rose, Lotus, Banana, Mango, Rose UK"
the category dropdown should not contain main categories "Flower, Fruits, Herbs"

name: Plant Category Selection
description:
As an admin
  I want to see only sub-categories in the plant category dropdown
  So that I can classify plants correctly

steps.name: user is logged in as admin
user is on the Plants List page

elements.name: Verify Admin can successfully add a new plant with valid data

steps.name: user clicks on "Add a Plant" button
user should be navigated to "Add Plants" page
user enters plant name as "Red Rose"
user selects sub category as "Rose UK"
user enters price as "2000"
user enters quantity as "12"
user clicks on "save" button
a success message "Plant added successfully" should be displayed
user should be redirected to "/ui/plants" page
newly added plant "Red Rose" should be displayed in the plants list
